lmn-gpo (1.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rename for consistency with the lmn-gpo command: the Python module is now
    lmn_gpo (was lmgpo), the source launcher is lmn-gpo-cli, and the client check
    script is lmn-gpo-check.ps1.
  * Config directory moved to /etc/linuxmuster/lmn-gpo/ (was /etc/linuxmuster/lmgpo/).
    An existing site.yaml at the old path is migrated on install and is still read
    from a source checkout as a fallback — no settings are lost.

 -- Kevin Stenzel <kevin@ks98.de>  Mon, 13 Jul 2026 13:00:00 +0000

lmn-gpo (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package of the linuxmuster-gpo-template toolkit.
  * Installs the lmn-gpo CLI (/usr/bin/lmn-gpo), the lmgpo Python module and the
    read-only policy data under /usr/share/lmn-gpo (catalog, scripts, lib).
  * Reads its configuration from /etc/linuxmuster/lmgpo/site.yaml; an existing
    site.yaml from a previous source checkout is migrated on install.

 -- Kevin Stenzel <kevin@ks98.de>  Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0000
